title: Giadas Holiday Handbook S01E03 Friendsgiving Party PDTV.x264-JIV
description:
Giada's Holiday Handbook - Season 1, Episode 3




Friendsgiving Party

Giada De Laurentiis hosts a cocktail-style Thanksgiving celebration to honor and thank her closest friends. Rather than a sit-down dinner, all the dishes are appetizer-sized versions of beloved holiday dishes, like Stuffing Arancini, Turkey Waldorf Bites, Charred Brussels Sprout Crostini and a Mulled Cosmo cocktail.




Original Air Date: 22-Nov-2015
